Maybe look at yourself and your bf, you're not exactly been that nice either.
All I ever did in the first place was comment on shitty smilies, because that's what I do.

I never intend to hurt individuals, I just comment on whatever the fuck I feel like, and you just happened to be the one posting it.

I express my disinterest in everything pretty much, and if you're not fine with that then I can't force you to be. We're simply just two people who work differently.

If you don't think I know how depression works, you're on the wrong track. I've had meds for like 11+ years, but the difference here is that I tend _not_ to talk about it because I see no reason to do so. Tell me if you can, what is the point of bringing it up in the first place? I only did for this very discussion.
